column2: Delicious cookies! Eat them warm from the oven.
This blueberry cobbler is an excellent light dessert that isn't too sweet! This recipe works great with all types of fruit. Serve with whipped cream or vanilla ice cream.
This delicious stuffed eggplant with a cheesy top is a must-try recipe! Great as a hearty main but you can buy the mini eggplants and use them for a side dish or appetizer.
I really like this recipe. It's a lot easier and fewer calories than traditional fried eggplant Parmesan.
The best of both worlds! Sweet, savory, and absolutely delicious.

column1: Overnight Steel-Cut Oats with Yogurt and Blueberries
column2: Overnight steel-cut oats with yogurt, stevia powder, coconut milk, and blueberries.
This blueberry pie, made with fresh berries, is a beautiful sight with a lattice top.
